### Hadith 3:353

*Narrated 'Abdullah bin 'Umar:*

Allah's Apostle forbade the sale called 'Habal-al-Habala which was a
kind of sale practiced in the Pre-lslamic Period of ignorance. One would
pay the price of a she-camel which was not born yet would be born by the
immediate offspring of an extant she-camel.

